I made this map to startup a completele new concept, Maps for warmup!

Simply play this online with friends, or as i preffer with your friends play against bots that you filled up the opposing team with.

(NAV is included for playing against bots)

Basicly its a great way to get warmed up with its tested online and everybody seems happy with it and the idea of maps for that kind of stuff.

So i can now Proudly say I started the warmup map concept :)

(CS:S) (18 Spawns in all) Author: Proxe
